  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/765fc3d8ce06c93aa076c056722335296cef8c08" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -3.005ex; width:23.076ex; height:7.509ex;" alt="\lambda = \frac{h}{p} = \frac {h}{{m}{v}} \sqrt{1 - \frac{v^2}{c^2}}"/></span></dd></dl>
<p>où <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \lambda }">
